org.cpsolver.ifs.util

Class Query

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.util.Query
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Query
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A representation of a boolean query. Besides of AND, OR, and NOT, the query may also contain terms (such as major:M1) that are evaluated by the Query.TermMatcher.
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)
